description:
Storage Hunters, Season 3, Episode 8 or Episode 6.
Title: Winter Wonderland.

First aired on July 8, 2013.

Description: A trip to Lake Arrowhead brings rain, snow and a new couple who drive Brandori crazy.

Note: there seems to be some mixe-up in the episodes numbering for season 3.  Episode 8 is the original number for the downloaded file but Episode 6 is the most likely right number that I found on the web from its description.  I've also added the title to the original file's name.

Second note: I won't upload the Episode S03E07/s03e04 (Lock and Load ("T Money wins a mysterious bin with a massive, chained up steel door.")) because this is the same as the episode S03E7 already uploaded by TvTeam and Sceneline.
